---
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Arcade FM · Jeux & Expériences</title>
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cinzel:wght@400;700;900&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap');

    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --bg:        #07090f;
      --surface:   #0d1120;
      --surface2:  #131829;
      --border:    rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
      --gold:      #d4a017;
      --gold-dim:  #a07810;
      --violet:    #7c5cbf;
      --violet-glow: rgba(124,92,191,0.25);
      --text:      #e8e0d0;
      --muted:     #7a8090;
      --tag-full:  #1a2d1a;
      --tag-full-c:#4ade80;
      --tag-mini:  #1a1a2d;
      --tag-mini-c:#818cf8;
    }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      min-height: 100vh;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    body::before {
      content: '';
      position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 0;
      background-image:
        linear-gradient(rgba(212,160,23,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(212,160,23,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 60px 60px;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    header {
      position: relative; z-index: 10;
      padding: 3rem 2rem 2rem;
      text-align: center;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .site-back {
      position: absolute; top: 1.5rem; left: 2rem;
      font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--muted);
      text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }
    .site-back:hover { color: var(--gold); }
    .site-back::before { content: '← '; }

    .header-title {
      font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gold) 0%, #f5d060 50%, var(--gold-dim) 100%);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
      line-height: 1.1;
      margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
    }

    .header-sub {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    main {
      position: relative; z-index: 1;
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 3rem 1.5rem 5rem;
    }

    .section-label {
      font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.3em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1rem;
    }
    .section-label::after {
      content: '';
      flex: 1;
      height: 1px;
      background: var(--border);
    }

    .featured-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
    }

    .card-featured {
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: inherit;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      position: relative;
      transition: transform 0.25s ease, box-shadow 0.25s ease, border-color 0.25s ease;
    }

    .card-featured:hover {
      transform: translateY(-4px);
      box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.5), 0 0 0 1px var(--gold-dim);
      border-color: var(--gold-dim);
    }

    .card-featured--violet:hover {
      box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.5), 0 0 0 1px var(--violet);
      border-color: var(--violet);
    }

    .card-featured::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
      height: 3px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--gold), transparent);
      opacity: 0;
      transition: opacity 0.3s;
    }
    .card-featured--violet::before {
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--violet), transparent);
    }
    .card-featured:hover::before { opacity: 1; }

    .card-banner {
      height: 160px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
      font-size: 3rem;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: var(--surface2);
    }

    .card-banner--fda {
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 60% 40%, #3a2a10 0%, #1a1205 100%);
    }
    .card-banner--eryndor {
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 40% 60%, #1a1030 0%, #0d0818 100%);
    }

    .card-banner img {
      width: 100px; height: auto;
      opacity: 0.9;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 0 20px rgba(212,160,23,0.4));
    }

    .card-banner-icon {
      font-size: 4rem;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 0 12px currentColor);
    }
    .card-banner--fda .card-banner-icon { color: var(--gold); }
    .card-banner--eryndor .card-banner-icon { color: #a78bfa; }
    .card-banner--orbique .card-banner-icon { color: #38bdf8; }
    .card-banner--orbique { background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 50%, #0c1e30 0%, #060d18 100%); }
    .card-featured--cyan:hover { box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.5), 0 0 0 1px #38bdf8; border-color: #38bdf8; }
    .card-featured--cyan::before { background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #38bdf8, transparent); }
    .card-featured--cyan .card-cta { color: #38bdf8; }

    .card-body {
      padding: 1.4rem 1.5rem 1.6rem;
      flex: 1;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.6rem;
    }

    .card-tag {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.35rem;
      font-size: 0.68rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem;
      border-radius: 4px;
      width: fit-content;
    }
    .card-tag--full {
      background: var(--tag-full);
      color: var(--tag-full-c);
      border: 1px solid rgba(74,222,128,0.2);
    }
    .card-tag--mini {
      background: var(--tag-mini);
      color: var(--tag-mini-c);
      border: 1px solid rgba(129,140,248,0.2);
    }
    .card-tag--soon {
      background: #2d1f0a;
      color: #f59e0b;
      border: 1px solid rgba(245,158,11,0.25);
    }
    .card-tag::before { content: '●'; font-size: 0.5rem; }

    .card-title {
      font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #f0e8d8;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }

    .card-desc {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.6;
      flex: 1;
    }

    .card-cta {
      margin-top: 0.8rem;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--gold);
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.4rem;
      transition: gap 0.2s;
    }
    .card-featured--violet .card-cta { color: #a78bfa; }
    .card-featured:hover .card-cta { gap: 0.7rem; }
    .card-cta::after { content: '→'; }

    .mini-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(220px, 1fr));
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    .card-mini {
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 1.2rem 1.3rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: inherit;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      transition: transform 0.2s, border-color 0.2s, background 0.2s;
    }
    .card-mini:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      background: var(--surface2);
      border-color: rgba(129,140,248,0.35);
    }

    .card-wip {
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px dashed rgba(245,158,11,0.3);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 1.4rem 1.5rem;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.6rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: inherit;
      transition: transform 0.25s ease, border-color 0.25s ease, background 0.25s ease;
    }
    .card-wip:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      border-color: rgba(245,158,11,0.6);
      background: var(--surface2);
    }
    .card-wip-header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.7rem;
    }
    .card-wip-icon {
      font-size: 1.6rem;
      width: 42px; height: 42px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      background: var(--surface2);
      border-radius: 8px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(245,158,11,0.2);
    }
    .card-wip-title {
      font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #f0e0c0;
    }
    .card-wip-subtitle {
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      color: #f59e0b;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .card-wip-desc {
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .card-wip-refs {
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-style: italic;
      padding-top: 0.4rem;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      margin-top: 0.3rem;
    }

    .card-mini-header {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.7rem;
    }

    .card-mini-icon {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      width: 36px; height: 36px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      background: var(--surface2);
      border-radius: 8px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .card-mini-title {
      font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #d8d0e8;
    }

    .card-mini-desc {
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    footer {
      position: relative; z-index: 1;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2rem;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      color: var(--muted);
    }
    footer a { color: var(--gold); text-decoration: none; }
    footer a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      header { padding: 3.5rem 1rem 1.5rem; }
      .site-back { top: 1rem; left: 1rem; }
      main { padding: 2rem 1rem 4rem; }
      .card-banner { height: 120px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <a class="site-back" href="https://fmenguy.fr">fmenguy.fr</a>
  <div class="header-title">Arcade FM</div>
  <div class="header-sub">Jeux &amp; expériences web</div>
</header>

<main>

  <div class="section-label">Jeux complets</div>
  <div class="featured-grid">

    <a class="card-featured" href="/fda/">
      <div class="card-banner card-banner--fda">
        <img src="/fda/assets/fda.webp" alt="Forge des Âges" onerror="this.style.display='none';this.nextElementSibling.style.display='flex'">
        <span class="card-banner-icon" style="display:none">⚒</span>
      </div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <span class="card-tag card-tag--full">Jeu complet</span>
        <div class="card-title">Forge des Âges</div>
        <div class="card-desc">Jeu de gestion médiéval au tour par tour. Gérez vos ressources, explorez la carte, forgez votre empire. Avec ambiance sonore et mode mobile.</div>
        <span class="card-cta">Jouer</span>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a class="card-featured card-featured--violet" href="/eryndor/">
      <div class="card-banner card-banner--eryndor">
        <span class="card-banner-icon">⚔</span>
      </div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <span class="card-tag card-tag--full">Jeu complet</span>
        <div class="card-title">Eryndor : Duel d'IA</div>
        <div class="card-desc">Simulation fantasy en mode spectateur. Deux agents Claude s'affrontent à la tête des humains et des elfes. Apporte ta clé API au lancement.</div>
        <span class="card-cta">Jouer</span>
      </div>
    </a>

    <a class="card-featured card-featured--cyan" href="/orbique/">
      <div class="card-banner card-banner--orbique">
        <span class="card-banner-icon">🔵</span>
      </div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <span class="card-tag card-tag--full">Jeu complet</span>
        <div class="card-title">Orbique</div>
        <div class="card-desc">Jeu d'exploration en salles thématiques. Particules, textures, puzzles et tutoriel intégré pour une expérience visuelle immersive.</div>
        <span class="card-cta">Jouer</span>
      </div>
    </a>

  </div>

  <div class="section-label">Mini-jeux</div>
  <div class="mini-grid">

    <a class="card-mini" href="/zentel/">
      <div class="card-mini-header">
        <span class="card-mini-icon">🔮</span>
        <span class="card-mini-title">Zentel</span>
      </div>
      <div class="card-mini-desc">Expérimentation visuelle interactive générée avec p5.js.</div>
    </a>

    <a class="card-mini" href="/ecosim/ecosystem.html">
      <div class="card-mini-header">
        <span class="card-mini-icon">🌿</span>
        <span class="card-mini-title">EcoSim</span>
      </div>
      <div class="card-mini-desc">Simulation d'écosystème. Créatures, nourriture, prédateurs, observez l'équilibre se construire.</div>
    </a>

    <a class="card-mini" href="/conway/">
      <div class="card-mini-header">
        <span class="card-mini-icon">🧬</span>
        <span class="card-mini-title">Jeu de la Vie</span>
      </div>
      <div class="card-mini-desc">Automate cellulaire de Conway. Tracez des patterns et regardez la vie émerger.</div>
    </a>

  </div>

  <div class="section-label">En développement</div>
  <div class="featured-grid">

    <a class="card-wip" href="/strates/editor/">
      <div class="card-wip-header">
        <span class="card-wip-icon">🌍</span>
        <div>
          <div class="card-wip-title">Strates <span style="font-size:0.65rem;color:#7a8090;font-weight:400;">(titre provisoire)</span></div>
          <div class="card-wip-subtitle">Alpha très précoce</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card-wip-desc">
        Pré-démo d'un sandbox god-game inspiré de Godus, From Dust et Spore. Terrain voxel en strates, colons autonomes, premiers bâtiments. Tout reste à construire, mais c'est jouable.
      </div>
    </a>

  </div>

</main>

<footer>
  <p>Un projet de <a href="https://fmenguy.fr">François Menguy</a></p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
